 told someone what you want, to make sure that they have understood you and will obey you.\nYou do not hit my grandchildren, do you understand?...\nI don't need it, understand?...", '明白吗？懂了没有？\n你不准打我的孙子孙女，明白吗？\n我不需要，懂吗？']]}]